org.forgerock.openam.upgrade

Class ServiceSchemaModificationWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.upgrade.ServiceSchemaModificationWrapper

  • public class ServiceSchemaModificationWrapper
extends Object
    This class wraps the attribute modifications for a specific service schema and the attributes within the services schema schemas.
    Author:
    steve
